;;; Bitwise operations are translated into LOG-OPs with the
;;; appropriate bitfields.  Fill in the following truth table, and
;;; then construct a bitfield with the bits you get, as below.
;;; 
;;;              X
;;;            0   1
;;;           -------
;;;        0 | 8 | 4 |
;;;     Y    | - - - |
;;;        1 | 2 | 1 |
;;;           -------
;;;
;;;    #b8421

